{
  "stem": "19111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 243.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some of them asked them to come, and they would hide them and all that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they thought that they will perhaps, eventually, do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But once they lost their only child, Boris, they lost the entire feeling for living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They gave up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They did not want to continue to live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She walked around constantly, his mother, with his shirt, the last shirt that he wore, clutched up against her chest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 16 SECONDS] [DRINKS] It was a time of perhaps it was better to die right then and there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The insult, the bestiality, the tragedies that we had to live with every single moment is beyond, really, understanding.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Beyond even-- I don't even know how the heck some people endured it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were cases of suicide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was incomprehensible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from memory, I think that they were kept back by their parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, you must understand that the German-- the Nazi machinery has put a tremendous fear and fright into the Polish, and the Lithuanian residents as well, and they made a proclamation that anybody helping the Jews, hiding [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] be caught, they will be punished in the most severe way, and that meant death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were some cases like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So any one of the Gentiles who would have had to risk his life and the life of his family as well, to-- to help like this.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Lithuanians in particular were very, very brutal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They somehow in the thousands were very willing, and they were very helpful to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They probably thought that [INAUDIBLE] is going to be theirs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were promised that Lithuania will be an independent country, and towards that end, they did everything they could.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
